  <hr>
  <p style="margin: 5% 0 1%; padding: 0;"><i>OVERVIEW</i></p>

  <h2>
    A "focus timer" feature for SoundCloud's mobile application.
  </h2>
  <p>
     Primarily targted towards folks in their early
    20's, the core components of this feature include timer setting, playlist
    selection, and playlist sharing.
  </p>

